column6: The Last Days of Spider-Woman! Spider-Woman's roadtrip across the country continues, as she pays a visit to the Alamo! Not even Spider-Woman and her RAGTAG CREW OF BEN URICH AND THE PORCUPINE are safe from SECRET WARS, though.
column8: | artist:Natacha Bustos | writer:Dennis Hopeless | editor:Nick Lowe | penciller (cover):Javier Rodriguez
